e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:33:04.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<br />\n<br />\n幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b433039249a6076e3902ca840e7bd6b878ceb7f1","tid":165211,"uid":93264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打我有興趣， 想問下會唔會諗住去埋金剛山？<br />\n<br />\nglo 做左好耐北韓團，不過貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見佢今次好似無金剛山，有咩特別？GLO可能賣沈旭暉同埋其他帶隊，所以特別貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be181820f0ec094f51cc5e4d7bcb5c7f00404d6","tid":165211,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"一定係4月尾出發？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e23a54c2eaf3abde2d9f4a6c05542eb4f7f26e8","tid":165211,"uid":93264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定係4月尾出發？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今次好似係，唔知會唔會搞第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ff5f8ae08035f6111cf4feab5af9d96f31e4cf","tid":165211,"uid":12720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:21:01.000Z","msg":"tg : yyss5"},{"pid":"10d42880d51c47d790708e56c780c18f8913c5a4","tid":165211,"uid":63401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打我有興趣， 想問下會唔會諗住去埋金剛山？<br />\n<br />\nglo 做左好耐北韓團，不過貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見佢今次好似無金剛山，有咩特別？GLO可能賣沈旭暉同埋其他帶隊，所以特別貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n經元山去金剛山，以前係南北韓旅遊合作區，主要睇風景，有分外金剛同內金剛<br />\n<br />\n由平壤坐車要幾個鐘，因為太入，所以要起金剛山住一日"},{"pid":"e6f2c2f4bade10e0813f73364c5567ae1dda4ba9","tid":165211,"uid":887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5027698575b525437780ea5d514d3efbd5759c","tid":165211,"uid":93264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T12:54:00.000Z","msg":"ICIC<br />\n不過佢睇落無呢個行程"},{"pid":"8462786ee1a9d95c845c7327725b8def2cd9dea3","tid":165211,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T12:59:50.000Z","msg":"$15000<br />\nOn9<br />\n番大陸包團平一半有多<br />\n一樣瀋陽出入"},{"pid":"4661c15ac87226a64554858c562724ea4ef51834","tid":165211,"uid":64956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>$15000<br />\nOn9<br />\n番大陸包團平一半有多<br />\n一樣瀋陽出入</blockquote><br />\n用大陸護照先平唔係咩?<br />\n香港護照邊有得平"},{"pid":"31c0fdf4f372f49ee00ff34c30e00329d001d670","tid":165211,"uid":93264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T13:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>$15000<br />\nOn9<br />\n番大陸包團平一半有多<br />\n一樣瀋陽出入</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大陸團行程係點架？"}]}